<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Remarcar Visita • MatchImóveis</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    * { box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }
    body { font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif; background:#f5f5f5; color:#222; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; min-height:100vh; }
    .card { background:#fff; border-radius:20px; padding:40px 32px; box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.10); max-width:420px; width:90%; }
    .logo { color:#ff385c; font-size:18px; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:28px; display:block; }
    h1 { font-size:22px; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .sub { color:#666; font-size:14px; margin-bottom:28px; }
    .info-row { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; padding:12px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6; font-size:15px; }
    .info-label { color:#888; }
    .info-val { font-weight:600; }
    .aviso { background:#fff7ed; border:1px solid #fed7aa; border-radius:12px; padding:14px 16px; margin:24px 0; font-size:14px; color:#92400e; }
    .form-group { margin-top:20px; }
    .form-group label { display:block; font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:#555; margin-bottom:6px; }
    .form-group input { width:100%; padding:12px 14px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:10px; font-size:15px; outline:none; }
    .form-group input:focus { border-color:#f59e0b; box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(245,158,11,.15); }
    .btn { display:block; width:100%; padding:16px; border-radius:12px; border:none; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; cursor:pointer; margin-top:24px; background:#f59e0b; color:#fff; }
    .btn:hover { background:#d97706; }
    .success { margin-top:28px; text-align:center; }
    .success .icon { font-size:56px; }
    .success p { font-weight:700; font-size:18px; margin-top:12px; }
    .success .desc { color:#666; margin-top:8px; font-size:14px; font-weight:400; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <span class="logo">MatchImóveis</span>

    <% if (sucesso) { %>
      <div class="success">
        <div class="icon">📅</div>
        <p>Nova data enviada!</p>
        <p class="desc">O corretor receberá sua solicitação e confirmará em breve.</p>
      </div>
    <% } else { %>

      <h1>Remarcar visita</h1>
      <p class="sub">Escolha uma nova data e horário para visitar o imóvel.</p>

      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Imóvel</span><span class="info-val"><%= visita.imovelTitulo || visita.imovelBairro || 'Imóvel' %></span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Bairro</span><span class="info-val"><%= visita.imovelBairro %> - <%= visita.imovelCidade %></span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Data anterior</span><span class="info-val" style="color:#ef4444"><%= visita.dataVisita || '-' %></span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Horário anterior</span><span class="info-val" style="color:#ef4444"><%= visita.horaVisita || '-' %></span></div>

      <div class="aviso">
        ⚠️ O dia e horário anteriores não estão disponíveis. Escolha uma nova opção abaixo.
      </div>

      <form method="POST" action="/cliente/visita/<%= visita.id %>/remarcar">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Nova data</label>
          <input type="date" name="novaData" required min="<%= new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0] %>">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Novo horário</label>
          <input type="time" name="novoHorario" required min="07:00" max="20:00">
        </div>
        <button class="btn" type="submit">📅 Confirmar nova data</button>
      </form>

    <% } %>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
